S = (x+1)(x+2)+(x+3)(x+4)+\cdots+(x+99)(x+100)
S = \sum_{r=1}^{99}(x+r)(x+r+1)
S = \sum_{r=1}^{99}\frac{(x+r)(x+r+1)((x+r+2)-(x+r-1))}{(x+r+2)-(x+r-1)}
S = \sum_{r=1}^{99}\frac{(x+r)(x+r+1)((x+r+2)-(x+r-1))}{3}
S = \frac{1}{3}\sum_{r=1}^{99}(x+r)(x+r+1)(x+r+2)-(x+r-1)(x+r)(x+r+1)
